data.description:
This charming single-family home located in a corner lot within the highly sought-after Counterpoint Estates community. With no HOA fees. This home features 4 bedrooms 3 baths, Open floor plan with high ceilings in the main living area, and tile floors throughout. The kitchen captures every chef's dream, featuring Quartz countertops, wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and a stylish farmfront apron sink. Recent upgrades include; walking closets, new wide crown molding, baseboards, new doors, insulation, fresh paint, floors, blinds, irrigation, and landscaping, ensuring a pristine and welcoming environment. A/C 2023, Water heater 2023, Solar Panel 2023, Pool and outside area 2023. The property is fully fenced. The backyard is a serene retreat, featuring a brand new saltwater Swimming Pool surrounded by pavers and artificial grass, creating a low-maintenance oasis perfect for outdoor enjoyment and gatherings.

Residents of Counterpoint Estates enjoy access to multiple playgrounds within the community, adding to the family-friendly ambiance. The neighborhood's convenient location places it close to fine dining establishments, movie theaters, and Wellington Mall. With easy access to Downtown West Palm Beach and the airport. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful property your new home sweet home.
